Class HantoBoard

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mygdx.hanto.implementation.common.HantoBoard

  • public class HantoBoard
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the board for all the the Hanto Game. This is basically a map to map the HantoPice with their coordinate on the current Hanto Game.

    Author:
